<i>noun</i>: 치매 [치매] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>치매 [치매]</dt><br>
<dd>dementia; Alzheimer's disease</dd><br>
<dd>주로 노인에게 나타나며, 뇌세포가 손상되어 지능, 의지, 기억 등이 사라지는 병.</dd><br>
<dd>A disease, usually affecting the elderly, which damages brains cells and leads to loss of intelligence, will, memory, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>